      "text": "<<container>> app  (Java 21 + Spring Boot 3)\nImage: tinyurl-app:latest\n(Gradle multi-stage → eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine)\nPort: 8080 (internal only — not host-mapped)\nEnv: BASE_URL, LOG_LEVEL\nSecrets: /tinyurl/prod/* via AWS SSM Parameter Store (IAM Role)\nDepends on: pgbouncer (healthy), redis (healthy) (v2)\nHealth check: GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health",
