      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "<<container>> postgres\nImage: postgres:16-alpine\nPort: 5432 (internal only — exposed 5433:5432 for dev)\nVolumes: pg-data:/var/lib/postgresql/data\n         ./migrations/ → /docker-entrypoint-initdb.d/\nEnv: POSTGRES_DB=tinyurl, POSTGRES_USER, POSTGRES_PASSWORD\nHealth check: pg_isready -U tinyurl",
